WEBVTT

00:03.770 --> 00:05.624
MRS. FREUDLICH,

00:05.630 --> 00:07.734
TELL ME WHAT YOU DON'T LIKE
ABOUT YOURSELF.

00:07.740 --> 00:09.139
IT'S BERGER.

00:09.140 --> 00:10.505
I'M BLISS BERGER.

00:10.510 --> 00:12.808
