UH, 4:00, SEAN.

00:12.810 --> 00:14.778
I'M SORRY, MY MISTAKE.

00:14.780 --> 00:16.042
MISS BERGER,

00:16.050 --> 00:17.870
TELL US WHAT YOU DON'T
LIKE ABOUT YOURSELF.

00:17.880 --> 00:20.144
MY WINGS.

00:21.680 --> 00:23.341
MAY WE SEE YOUR WINGS?

00:26.420 --> 00:28.684
I CALL THIS THE
WA'I'I'LE FROM HELL.

00:28.690 --> 00:29.952
WHEN IT'S HOT,

00:29.960 --> 00:31.279
I JUST MOVE IT BACK
AND FORTH LIKE THIS,

00:31.290 --> 00:33.224
AND IN 20 SECONDS
MY CONDO'S COOLER

00:33.230 --> 00:34.925
THAN AN ICE CREAM TRUCK.
I SWEAR TO GOD.

00:34.930 --> 00:37.228
AND THAT'S JUST MY ARM.

00:37.230 --> 00:38.561
DO YOU WANT TO SEE
MY BACK FAT?

00:38.570 --> 00:41.494
YOUR POINT'S BEEN
EFFECT IVELY MADE, MISS BERGER.

00:41.500 --> 00:43.104
YOU CAN PUT YOUR JACKET ON
IF YOU WISH.

00:43.110 --> 00:44.407
THANK YOU.

00:44.410 --> 00:47.004
