OPERATION YOU WANT

00:52.350 --> 00:54.238
IS CALLED A BRACHIOPLASTY.

00:54.250 --> 00:57.242
WE CAN PROBABLY DO THE
ABDOMNIOPLASTY AT THE SAME TIME?

00:57.250 --> 00:58.945
PUT IT ON THE BOOKS.

00:58.950 --> 01:00.383
