IN VERA WANG.

01:03.760 --> 01:05.227
HEH HEH.
IS THERE A DATE?

01:05.230 --> 01:06.458
BECAUSE THERE WILL BE
A HEALING PERIOD,

01:06.460 --> 01:08.655
