TALKING SLEEVELESS.

01:08.660 --> 01:10.218
NO DATE YET.

01:10.230 --> 01:13.028
UM, THAT'S WHY I'M HERE.

01:13.040 --> 01:15.759
I MET MY SOUL MATE
ON JDATE.COM.

01:15.770 --> 01:17.965
LOOK.

01:17.970 --> 01:20.074
THIS IS MY ISAAC.

01:20.080 --> 01:21.900
IS HE NOT TO DIE?

01:21.910 --> 01:23.969
NOT ONLY IS HE
GOOD-LOOKING

01:23.980 --> 01:26.119
AND JEWISH,
HE'S A DOCTOR.

01:26.120 --> 01:29.317
WE'VE BEEN DATING
FOR 6 MONTHS NOW...

01:29.320 --> 01:31.208
