01:32.260 --> 01:34.717
HE HASN'T SEEN YOU YET?

01:34.720 --> 01:37.985
NO, OF COURSE HE HAS.
I SENT HIM A PICTURE...

01:37.990 --> 01:39.719
THAT'S 10 YEARS OLD.

01:39.730 --> 01:42.528
