ME TIPPING THE SCALES

01:42.530 --> 01:45.124
AT 260, YOU KNOW.
HE'D REJECT ME.

01:45.130 --> 01:47.928
HE IS VERY INTO
PHYSICAL FITNESS.

01:47.940 --> 01:50.238
