01:51.670 --> 01:53.501
AND NOW HE'S PUSHING
FOR A MEETING?

01:53.510 --> 01:55.671
HAS BEEN FOR
3 MONTHS NOW,

01:55.680 --> 01:56.908
SO I GOT MOTIVATED

01:56.910 --> 01:58.343
AND LOST THE JUNK
IN THE TRUNK.

01:58.350 --> 02:00.011
BUT NOW I HAVE
A DEADLINE.

02:00.020 --> 02:01.976
WE'RE FINALLY
MEETING IN 3 WEEKS,

02:01.980 --> 02:03.618
AND I HAVE GOT
TO LOOK HOT.

02:03.620 --> 02:07.158
SO, MISS BERGER,
YOU'VE BEEN LIVING A LIE.

02:09.760 --> 02:13.389
OK...YEAH...I HAVE BEEN.

02:13.400 --> 02:15.960
AND I'M ASHAMED
ABOUT THAT.

02:15.960 --> 02:17.496
IT WAS NOT RIGHT
TO LIE,

02:17.500 --> 02:18.922
BUT I AM WORKING
VERY HARD

02:18.930 --> 02:20.192
TO MAKE IT
THE TRUTH.

02:20.200 --> 02:23.033
THEN LET'S MAKE
AN HONEST WOMAN OUT OF YOU.

02:23.040 --> 02:26.532
OK.

02:26.540 --> 02:27.837
YOU AND JULIA
BEEN SUCKING BACK

02:27.840 --> 02:29.239
A LITTLE CHARDONNAY
IN THE WINE CELLAR?

02:29.250 --> 02:30.547
YOU'VE BEEN AT HALF
MAST ALL DAY TODAY.

02:30.550 --> 02:32.609
I'M JUST TIRED,
THAT'S ALL.

02:32.620 --> 02:34.349
BAT GIRL GOT ME THINKING
ABOUT A SLOGAN

02:34.350 --> 02:36.409
FOR AN AD CAMPAIGN:
"BE YOURSELF.

02:36.420 --> 02:37.819
YOU KNOW YOU COULD
LOOK BETTER."

02:37.820 --> 02:39.014
GOOD, HUH?

02:39.020 --> 02:41.409
I TOLD YOU I DON'T WANT
TO ADVERTISE. IT'S SLEAZY.

02:41.420 --> 02:43.183
IT MAY HAVE BEEN SLEAZY
2 MONTHS AGO,

02:43.190 --> 02:44.487
BUT NOW IT'S
A NECESSITY.

02:44.490 --> 02:46.082
BOBOLIT'S DOUBLED
HIS BILLBOARD CAMPAIGN,

02:46.090 --> 02:47.159
