04:30.500 --> 04:34.129
THE BABY THAT MOM LOST.

04:34.140 --> 04:37.439
I WAS HOPING
IT WAS A BROTHER.

04:38.640 --> 04:40.938
THAT'S WHY YOU'RE SAD,
TOO, RIGHT?

04:40.940 --> 04:44.205
YOU CAN'T STOP THINKING
ABOUT IT, EITHER.

04:44.210 --> 04:47.179
I'M CONCERNED HOW
YOUR MOTHER FEELS.

04:47.180 --> 04:48.716
