06:17.440 --> 06:21.979
I WANTED TO NAME HIM DAVID.

06:21.980 --> 06:24.505
MY SONS MATI' AND DAVID.

06:29.950 --> 06:33.010
[CRYING]

06:39.660 --> 06:42.458
