BUT I DIGRESS.

07:35.950 --> 07:38.612
I DIDN'T TRASH YOUR CARS,
CHRISTIAN.

07:38.620 --> 07:39.814
YOU'RE GONNA HAVE TO FILE
A RESTRAINING ORDER

07:39.820 --> 07:41.856
AGAINST NAN ETI'E BABCOCK.

07:43.260 --> 07:44.557
SHE'S DEAD.

07:44.560 --> 07:47.324
