07:47.330 --> 07:49.628
WHICH MAKES YOU
THE PRIME SUSPECT.

07:55.640 --> 07:57.107
WHAT WOULD MY MOTIVE BE?

07:57.110 --> 07:58.532
YOU WANT THE POWER,
AND I'VE GOT IT.

07:58.540 --> 07:59.609
YOU'VE ENJOYED PUSHING
MY BUTTONS

07:59.610 --> 08:00.770
SINCE YOU STARTED HERE.

08:00.780 --> 08:02.407
