FOR RIDLEY, RIGHT?

10:34.330 --> 10:37.163
BECAUSE THOSE ARE
YOUR FEELINGS FOR ME.

10:37.170 --> 10:39.024
SO?

10:40.040 --> 10:41.689
SO HELP ME.

10:41.700 --> 10:43.668
YOU'RE THE ONLY ONE
I TRUST.

10:44.940 --> 10:49.741
HELP ME MAKE HER SATISFIED
SO I CAN KEEP HER.

10:51.810 --> 10:57.112
AND...I'LL SATISFY...YOU.

10:57.120 --> 11:01.056
WHAT, YOU'RE--YOU'RE
PROPOSING A 3-WAY?

11:01.060 --> 11:03.051
YES.

11:06.360 --> 11:08.191
HEY, HONEY.

11:08.200 --> 11:09.724
YOU MUST BE HUNGRY.

11:09.730 --> 11:11.664
