12:05.750 --> 12:06.751
MMM...

12:06.760 --> 12:09.479
MMM...MMM...

12:12.730 --> 12:15.858
ARE YOU HARD?

12:17.700 --> 12:19.793
OH...

12:19.800 --> 12:21.791
IS YOUR THING IN?

12:21.800 --> 12:24.837
