WHEN IT FAILED US.

12:24.840 --> 12:28.298
I JUST HAD MY PERIOD.
I SHOULD BE FINE.

12:28.310 --> 12:30.107
MMM...

12:33.780 --> 12:37.045
I CAN'T RISK FINE,
JULIA.

12:40.120 --> 12:43.385
I CAN'T GO THROUGH...
ANOTHER ACCIDENT.

12:47.460 --> 12:49.792
WE HAVE TO DO SOMETHING.

12:51.000 --> 12:55.699
