A VASECTOMY.

12:55.700 --> 12:58.498
THEN WE WOULDN'T HAVE
TO WORRY ANYMORE.

12:58.510 --> 13:01.900
THAT'S AN AWFULLY BIG LEAP...

13:01.910 --> 13:04.947
BETWEEN SOMETHING
AND VASECTOMY.

13:09.350 --> 13:11.784
BE HONEST, JULIA.

13:11.790 --> 13:15.055
DO YOU WANT
ANOTHER CHILD?

13:15.060 --> 13:17.119
CAN YOU SEE US
HAVING ONE?

13:23.500 --> 13:26.025
NO.

13:31.170 --> 13:35.675
MAYBE I SHOULD GET
MY TUBES TIED.

13:35.680 --> 13:39.400
THAT'S ABSURD.

13:39.410 --> 13:42.447
