PICKED OUT?

13:52.560 --> 13:54.425
HEH.

13:54.430 --> 13:59.868
NO. DID YOU?

13:59.870 --> 14:02.293
NO.

14:13.750 --> 14:14.876
SHE WANTS A 3-WAY?

14:14.880 --> 14:17.781
YEAH, HER GIRLFRIEND
MISSES GUYS.

14:17.790 --> 14:19.883
SO NOW YOU WANT
SOME ADVICE.

14:19.890 --> 14:21.653
SUDDENLY THE YEARNING
FOR UNCLE CHRISTIAN

14:21.660 --> 14:23.924
MAKES PERFECT SENSE.

14:26.830 --> 14:28.923
I'VE MISSED YOU.

14:28.930 --> 14:30.022
I REALLY HAVE.

14:30.030 --> 14:31.895
DID YOU TELL YOUR MOTHER

14:31.900 --> 14:32.992
WE WERE TAKING THE BOAT
OUT TODAY?

14:33.000 --> 14:34.069
OF COURSE NOT, MAN.

14:34.070 --> 14:35.059
SHE WOULD HAVE
HIT THE ROOF.

14:35.070 --> 14:36.537
SHE HAD EVERY RIGHT TO.

14:36.540 --> 14:38.633
I SHOULD NEVER HAVE TAKEN YOU
TO THAT PORN PARTY, MA'IT.

14:38.640 --> 14:39.800
IF YOU AND I ARE GONNA HANG,

14:39.810 --> 14:41.038
WE'RE FOLLOWING
A NEW SET OF RULES.

14:41.040 --> 14:43.201
NO MORE ILLICIT CONVERSATIONS,

14:43.210 --> 14:44.939
NO MORE ADVICE ON THINGS

14:44.950 --> 14:47.874
